rules.description: [SpaceFN] Space+f -> Cmd+space (spotlight), Space+s -> Cmd+Tab (switch app), Space+. -> Ctrl+space (change input source)
SpaceFN: Space+[1-9] to F[1-9], Space+0 to F10, Space+Hyphen (-) to F11, Space+Equal Sign (=) to F12, Space+m to Backtick (`), Space+Comma to Tilde (~)
SpaceFN: Space+p to Cmd+shift+p (VScode control panel)
